Titolo: ATR: All Terrain Racing

Anno: 1995

Descrizione: ATR: All Terrain Racing is a racing game published by Team17 for Amiga and Amiga CD32 in 1995. During a protracted dispute between Team17 and Amiga Power, the magazine's reviewer, Jonathan Nash, awarded ATR: All Terrain Racing a rating of 38%, prompting the developer to pursue a lawsuit for defamation.